No. 32. Ross, Receiver, v. Knott, Treasurer of Florida, et al. October 4, 1937. M. G. McNair, present Receiver of the First National Bank of Perry, substituted as the party petitioner in place of Iron Ross, former Receiver, on motion of Mr. George P. Barse for the petitioner.
